|Resistor (for LDR)|1|10kΩ|"10K Ohm Resistor"|₹5-10|
|Resistor (for LED)|3-5|220Ω|"220 Ohm Resistor Pack"|₹20-40|
|Breadboard|1|400/830 points|"Breadboard 830 points"|₹80-150|
